Class MusicStringRenderer

java.lang.Object
  org.jfugue.MusicStringRenderer
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.EventListener, ParserListener
public final class MusicStringRenderer
extends java.lang.Object
implements ParserListener

This class is used to build a Pattern (i.e., a MusicString) given a MIDI Sequence.
